# Athens Tech Kit
**Outside Inn Studios | Mar–May 2026 | Living Document**

> Single reference for all hardware in Athens. Optimized for Notion, GitHub, and AI project context. Update this file when anything changes.

---

## Primary Machine

| Field | Value |
|---|---|
| **Device** | GIGABYTE AERO X16 1WH — OutsideInnHQ |
| **CPU** | AMD Ryzen AI 7 350 (8c/16t, up to 5GHz) |
| **GPU** | NVIDIA RTX 5070 Laptop (8GB GDDR7) — driver 595.79 WHQL |
| **RAM** | 32GB DDR5 5600MHz — memory diagnostic clean ✅ |
| **OS** | Windows 11 Home 64-bit |
| **Display** | 16" IPS 2560×1600 165Hz (16:10) |
| **Ports** | 1× USB4/USB-C (DP 1.4, PD 3.0), 1× HDMI 2.1, 2× USB-A 3.2, 1× USB-A 2.0, RJ45 |

> ⚠️ Only one USB-C port on device. Anker hub occupies it during streaming.
> ⚠️ OBS canvas mismatch: laptop is 2560×1600 (16:10), OBS is 1920×1080 (16:9). Workaround: ZenScreen as broadcast display via DisplayLink, OR drop Windows res to 1920×1080 before streaming.
> ⚠️ GiMATE must stay in **Optimus mode**. ECO mode disables the dGPU entirely — never use it.

