## Display Setup

| Item | Role | Connection |
|---|---|---|
| **AERO X16 built-in** (2560×1600) | OBS dashboard + monitoring | — |
| **ASUS ZenScreen MB16ACV** (1920×1080) | Broadcast display — game + writing content | USB-C to USB-A → Anker hub → DisplayLink |

**Camera placement:** Elgato Facecam MK.2 mounts on top of ZenScreen — maintains eye contact with viewers while gaming or writing.

**OBS capture method:** Display Capture pointed at ZenScreen. Do NOT use Game Capture — it injects into WoW's DirectX pipeline and worsens GPU crashes.

