## WoW + OBS Fixes (Confirmed March 17, 2026)

| Issue | Fix | Status |
|---|---|---|
| WoW crash on transmog/Warband UI | `-d3d11` in Battle.net Additional Command Line Arguments | ✅ Fixed |
| OBS Game Capture hooking into WoW DX pipeline | Switched to Window Capture, WoW in Borderless Windowed | ✅ Fixed |
| Daily BSODs — `nvlddmkm.sys_Blackwell` | DDU clean install → NVIDIA 595.79 WHQL | ✅ Fixed |
| GiMATE ECO mode disabling dGPU | Set to Optimus mode permanently | ✅ Fixed |
| OBS resolution mismatch | ZenScreen as dedicated broadcast display (1920×1080 native) | ✅ Fixed |

